            <p>
               <lb/> אלעזר בר יודן בר <unclear>ס</unclear>וסו </p>
         </div>
         <div type="translation" ana="#b1" xml:id="hamm0071.translation"
            corresp="#hamm0071.diplomatic #hamm0071.transcription">
            <p>El'azar son of Yudan son of Susu (or Qoso / Qusu)</p>
         </div>
      </body>
      <back>
         <div type="commentary" ana="b1">
            <p>"the name of a male individual, his father and grandfather — the last possibly in the
               form of a nickname. It is plausible that this individual had contributed to the
               community, its synagogue, or the floor and was honored with this inscription …"<lb/>
               This panel was destroyed when a column base was put through it during later
               construction.</p>
         </div>
